features: NO MORE FRUSTRATION - Ever get frustrated with buried seat belt buckles slowing you down? It's a hassle digging receptacles our from under the seat, especially with child restraints around. The Buckle Booster snaps around your receptacle in a second to ensure: your seat belt buckle doesn't get buried. Making your receptacle stand up and be easily accessible for future rides, this adult and kid-friendly tool transforms buckling into a breeze.

SEAT BELT NOW CLICKS EASILY - The Buckle Booster stabilizes your seat belt receptacle, so you can smoothly click the metal tongue in and you're ready to go. No more wobbly belt that is hard to hold while buckling. No more buried receptacle hiding smugly under the seat or behind car or booster seats.

RAISES YOUR BUCKLE - The trouble with buckling can be multifold: bad angle, inadequate space, too far to reach for the buckle. All of these can waste your time and cause knuckle scrapes. The Buckle Booster elevates and angles your seat belt receptacle so the belt metal tongue can click in smoothy and effortlessly. No more strain and struggle - buckle yourself and others quickly and without hassle!

BPA FREE MATERIAL - SAFE FOR ALL AGES - The BPA-free Buckle Booster allows you to buckle up with just one hand, whether you are in a hurry or have mobility challenges. Are you post-surgery, have arthritis or simply unable to spare a hand for buckling? The Buckle Booster lets you buckle yourself and others painlessly. Keeping the receptacle stable, you just need to click the metal tongue in and you're ready to go!

BUCKLE FASTER, BETTER. CLEVER! - Reaching from the side to buckle babies and others is frustratingly impossible because of the floppy buckles getting buried under seats. With three booster or car seats in the back, your buckling task can be impossible. With the Buckle Booster, made from safe materials, buckling loved ones in the back is easy! You can comfortably reach the receptacle, even between car / booster seats. Just one car seat or an adult in the back? Reach the elevated buckle in a snap!

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: The Lil Hugger Buckle Booster Seat Belt Receptacle Raiser Buckling babies and adults just got easy! With your Lil Hugger Wrap Around Buckle Booster, you'll be able to buckle yourself with one hand or buckle children in the back seat without struggle. The Lil Hugger Wrap Around Buckle Booster raises back seat receptacles to make it easy to buckle yourself or your child in. Due to its clever design and superior materials, the Lil Hugger Wrap Around Buckle Booster will improve your ability to buckle yourself and others. No more hassle and frustration buckling up in the back seat! It's also helpful if you are a caretaker for others, making car trips that much more manageable. It works great for the elderly and other passengers seeking independence, like someone who is post-surgery or injured passengers with limited range of motion.

Will the Lil Hugger Wrap Around Buckle Booster Work For Me? Yes! If your seat belt receptacles sit above the level of the back seat bench, then the Lil Hugger Wrap Around Buckle Booster is very likely to be a great fit in your car. Give it a try, and see if it solves your buckle accessibility challenges. If it doesn't, we're here to help. Yes! If your seat belt receptacle lives in a recessed cavity, but can be pulled up and out of the cavity, the Lil Hugger Wrap Around Buckle Booster is very likely to be a great fit in your car. In fact, the Buckle Booster will help keep the receptacle from falling back into this cavity every time you unbuckle, adding struggle and strain to get at it again. If it doesn't fit, we're here to help. No! Not for recessed buckles. If your back seat receptacle is in a recessed cavity and it has wiggle room, but there isn't enough room around the sides or it doesn't come out more than halfway from the cavity, the Buckle Booster will not work in your vehicle, we're sorry to say. No! Will not work for recessed snaps. If your back seat receptacle(s) sit deep in a recessed cavity, with the top of the receptacle flush with the level of the back seat bench, the Lil Hugger Wrap Around Buckle Booster will not work in your vehicle, we're sorry to say. This is a very common design in Teslas, but it also appears in other vehicles.

Will My Recessed Receptacle Work With the Buckle Booster Please use the image to the right as a guide to understand if your recessed receptacle will work with the Buckle Booster. Some recessed receptacles have a spacious area in which to move, with room for the Buckle Booster to go around them within the recessed area and still get the top of the receptacle clear of the Buckle Booster. In these cases, the Buckle Booster should work. In other cases, the recessed receptacle is snug in the back seat bench with no room on any side for a Buckle Booster and no way to pull the receptacle out of the recessed groove. If this is the case, unfortunately, the Buckle Booster is not suitable for this location.

Lil' Hugger Buckle Booster Installation Step 1 Stretch the Lil Hugger Buckle Booster out slightly around the seat belt receptacle you would like to raise Step 2 Ensure that it fits firmly at the base, allowing access to the (usually red) release button of the buckle Step 3 Fasten the seat belt with ease! If your receptacle is simply too tight to comfortably in the Lil Hugger Wrap Around Buckle Booster as you move it to the base, buckle the seat belt in and use the strap as leverage to maneuver the Buckle Booster into place.

Materials: BPA-Free, PVC-Free, Phthalate Free, Lead Free We take safety seriously, so we worked hard to use the safest material when designing the Buckle Booster. Silicone and TPE material are used to make pacifiers, baby bottle parts, and food preparation items like spatulas. The denser version of this same material provides stability for your seat belt buckle and easy access for you! Don't get any ideas, though - you or your kids should not eat or chew on the Buckle Booster. The installer must assess safety.

The Booster Seat's Friend The Lil Hugger Wrap Around Buckle Booster is ideal next to your child's booster seat. It prevents you from having to reach all the way over your child to buckle them in. Two Booster Seats Together If you have two booster seats next to each other, or a booster seat and a car seat, the Buckle Booster raises up both receptacles between them, helping prevent buckle crunch (the nasty scraping of knuckles on booster seats). Comes With Fun Safety Stickers These stickers will provide some extra joy for your children while also reminding them about the importance of car safety. It's Often the Simple Things It's a remarkably simple solution, but it will make all the difference as you seek to buckle your kids into the back seat of the car.
